metadata.name: Dark Angel
metadata.description: One of the hardest things in our lives is to be ourselves. Not giving in to the desires of the community in favor of changing one's identity. This is why the dark side of personality and the light side of personality persist in us. The dark side forces us to maintain a complex relationship within a need. The light side makes us beautiful and free. he dark angel lives in each of us. The dark angel is you.
